Whataboutcriterias
So, you undestand that some job should be done and how you will get money for that job. Job can be done well, can be done bad. How to ask more? Need criterias, witch are known and accepted by sides of agreement. Do you have agreement? Are they documented? Are they sighed by sides? Who are sides for public job as this book? People who read this, use this or think the same?
Agreement. Are you agree? Are you signed without full agree? Are you signed under pressure. Are you signed and not sure in other side(s). 
